58.000Z","msg":"我隻有時都會爬高逃走，出黎偷食生果，咬到一忽忽，食完就番籠附近等人放佢入籠，<br />\n熟晒路咁"},{"pid":"6646ed0ce16e43d5006d82cf5b12c84d8bf6c053","tid":206942,"uid":47433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T18:44:02.000Z","msg":"我都試過，個籠d「la」太疏，d bb跌咗出籠<br />\n<br />\nbtw bb好易死<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa1b1d5c1763837300ec29c40e1c84e2abde27a7","tid":206942,"uid":41440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T18:44:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我之前養個隻成日自己識開鐵閘走入條水道出去玩 但永遠夜晚都識自己返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n心裡完全無牽掛　吃粒種子煩盡棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c2c26731f2dfaefac4607d0b57a23f4a22b3e41","tid":206942,"uid":43492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T18:46:02.000Z","msg":"試過失蹤三日 佢自己走返入籠"},{"pid":"2c7dc698124524bd15455fd5efe20f017ad59080","tid":206942,"uid":36026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T18:51:41.000Z","msg":"睇到個post諗起以前養過隻好痴我<br />\n打開籠會出黎 但唔會行到離我好遠<br />\n不過都死左差唔多8年"},{"pid":"53a38147b2bac691bcc602c85e803ded125c1cd1","tid":206942,"uid":32396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T18:55:35.000Z","msg":"試過養到肥嘟嘟既走甩左成個星期<br />\n成屋都搵唔到<br />\n就估佢親我地出門口果時偷走出屋<br />\n最後問隔離屋一問就見佢係人地道鐵閘到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過瘦到得番骨"},{"pid":"d24e4b5e1c1e036023b4192e6e9cbfb2aba6561b","tid":206942,"uid":47433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T18:57:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過養到肥嘟嘟既走甩左成個星期<br />\n成屋都搵唔到<br />\n就估佢親我地出門口果時偷走出屋<br />\n最後問隔離屋一問就見佢係人地道鐵閘到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過瘦到得番骨</blockquote><br />\n陰公豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔見咗成個星期都搵得番真係好好彩"},{"pid":"8e11ef546e900a0c279858bd22aeedf08999afa5","tid":206942,"uid":43575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T18:58:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過養到肥嘟嘟既走甩左成個星期<br />\n成屋都搵唔到<br />\n就估佢親我地出門口果時偷走出屋<br />\n最後問隔離屋一問就見佢係人地道鐵閘到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過瘦到得番骨</blockquote><br />\n倉鼠係直腸動物，所以要keep住食野同便便。所以通常都唔可以餓親，你隻鼠鼠成個星期都無事己經好好彩"},{"pid":"acf7ee6d00eeb1d9724ec1049d6d5de76027f9ea","tid":206942,"uid":42191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T19:03:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我之前養個隻成日自己識開鐵閘走入條水道出去玩 但永遠夜晚都識自己返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n心裡完全無牽掛　吃粒種子煩盡棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n和我高飛　放心歡笑　樂就是美<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5bdb0a943f60bcf0790a53459324f8275103443","tid":206942,"uid":70453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T19:08:38.000Z","msg":"試下放其他鼠bb出黎睇下佢地會走去邊？ 佢地可能鍾意去埋啲差唔多嘅地方 (記得望實你放出黎嘅鼠bb!) 希望你可以快啲搵返佢地喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7639d6f64dc1856fe9b4796818dc77df5acebf4","tid":206942,"uid":102641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T23:16:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我之前養個隻成日自己識開鐵閘走入條水道出去玩 但永遠夜晚都識自己返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n哈姆太朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5758806a81cd55bc57bf316f4014b620c41012cc","tid":206942,"uid":48578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T00:52:39.000Z","msg":"我之前果隻夜晚逃走左，隔兩日係隔離屋搵翻，人地仲照顧得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />